AUTOVIZ

M t: AutoViz (Auto Visualization) l mt th vin m ngun m ca Python, c thit k t ng to cc biu v hnh nh ha d liu ch vi mt dng code. N phn tch dataset v chn loi biu ph hp (nh histogram, scatter plot, box plot, v.v.) da trn loi d liu (s, phn loi, thi gian).

u im:

  • Nhanh chng v d s dng, ph hp cho phn tch s b.
  • To nhiu loi visualization a dng, hin th ngay trong notebook (nh Jupyter).
  • H tr d liu ln v t ng pht hin mi quan h gia cc bin.

Chc nng chnh

  • T ng to biu : To cc biu (histogram, scatter, box plot, heatmap, v.v.) da trn loi d liu (s, phn loi, thi gian)
  • Phn tch tng quan: Hin th mi quan h gia cc bin s (heatmap) v phn tch c bn vi bin mc tiu.
  • X l d liu ln: T ng ly mu ngu nhin x l dataset ln.
  • Ty chnh u ra: Xut biu dng SVG, PNG, JPG hoc HTML; lu vo th mc hoc hin th trong Jupyter Notebook.
  • D s dng: Ch cn 1 dng code to ton b visualization.

Gii thiu b d liu

Phn tch tnh cch khch hng (Customer Personality Analysis) l qu trnh nghin cu chi tit v nhm khch hng l tng ca doanh nghip. Cng c ny gip cc cng ty:

  • Hiu su v khch hng: Nm bt c im nhn khu hc, hnh vi mua sm v mi quan tm c th
  • Ti u ha sn phm: iu chnh sn phm/dch v theo nhu cu tng phn khc khch hng
  • Tip th mc tiu: Thay v chi tin tip th sn phm mi cho mi khch hng trong c s d liu, doanh nghip c th:
  • Xc nh phn khc c kh nng mua hng cao nht
  • Tp trung ngn sch marketing vo nhm mc tiu ny
  • Ti u hiu qu ROI (t sut hon vn)
  • V d thc t: Mt thng hiu m phm c th s dng CPA phn bit gia:

Nhm khch hng tr (18-25 tui) quan tm sn phm chng mn

Nhm khch hng trung nin (35-50 tui) cn sn phm chng lo ha T xy dng chin dch marketing ring cho tng nhm i tng.

Cch s dng Autoviz

V d 1: Trc quan ha file CSV vi bin mc tiu

Mc tiu: To biu t ng cho file CSV vi bin mc tiu (target), s dng nh dng SVG v hin th log chi tit.

Tnh nng s dng:

  • T ng to biu .
  • Phn tch vi bin mc tiu (depVar='target').
  • nh dng u ra SVG.
  • Hin th log chi tit (verbose=1).
In[]:
from autoviz import AutoViz_Class
import warnings

# B qua cc cnh bo khng cn thit
warnings.filterwarnings("ignore", category=DeprecationWarning)
warnings.filterwarnings("ignore", category=FutureWarning)

# Khi to AutoViz
AV = AutoViz_Class()

filename = df  # Hoc ng dn ti file CSV
target_variable = "Response"

try:
    dft = AV.AutoViz(
        filename,
        sep=",",
        depVar=target_variable,
        dfte=None,
        header=0,
        verbose=1,
        lowess=False,
        chart_format="svg",
        max_rows_analyzed=150000,
        max_cols_analyzed=30,
        save_plot_dir=None
    )
except AttributeError as e:
    print(" B qua li v biu :", e)

on code trn dng AutoViz t ng phn tch d liu (EDA) cho bin mc tiu "Response". N khi to AutoViz_Class, tt cc cnh bo khng cn thit, ri chy phng thc AutoViz() to biu v thng k. D liu u vo c th l DataFrame hoc file CSV, vi gii hn 150.000 dng v 30 ct trnh qu ti. Tham s lowess=False tt lm mt scatter plot cho tc nhanh hn, chart_format="svg" xut biu r nt, v verbose=1 hin th thng tin mc va phi. Cui cng, save_plot_dir=None ngha l biu s khng c lu vo th mc ring m ch hin th trc tip trong mi trng chy.

V d 2: Trc quan ha mt dataframe pandas khng c bin mc tiu

Mc tiu: To biu cho DataFrame trc tip (khng dng file CSV) m khng c bin mc tiu, hin th trn server.

Tnh nng s dng:

  • H tr DataFrame trc tip (dfte=df).
  • To biu m khng cn bin mc tiu.
  • Hin th trn server (chart_format="server").
  • Hin th log chi tit (verbose=1).
In[]:
import pandas as pd
from autoviz import AutoViz_Class
AV = AutoViz_Class()

# To bo co cho DataFrame
dft = AV.AutoViz(
    filename="",                  # Khng dng file CSV
    sep=",",                     # Khng p dng v khng dng file
    depVar="",                   # Khng c bin mc tiu
    dfte=df,                     # Truyn DataFrame trc tip
    header=0,                    # Dng u tin l tiu 
    verbose=1,                   # Hin th log chi tit
    lowess=False,                # Khng s dng ng cong LOWESS
    chart_format="server",       # Hin th trn server
    max_rows_analyzed=150000,    # Gii hn s dng
    max_cols_analyzed=30,        # Gii hn s ct
    save_plot_dir=None           # Khng lu biu 
)

V d 3: To biu Bokeh tng tc v lu chng di dng tp HTML

Mc tiu: To biu tng tc Bokeh v lu vo th mc ty chnh vi bin mc tiu.

Tnh nng s dng:

  • To biu tng tc vi Bokeh (chart_format="bokeh").
  • Lu biu vo th mc ty chnh (save_plot_dir).
  • Phn tch vi bin mc tiu.
  • Lu ton b biu (verbose=2).
In[]:
# ============================================
#  V d 3: To biu  Bokeh tng tc v lu thnh HTML
# ============================================

# ---- 1. Import th vin ----
import pandas as pd
from bokeh.plotting import figure, output_file, save
from bokeh.models import HoverTool
import os

# ---- 2. c d liu ----
# Gi s dataset c cc ct: Year_Birth, Income, Response
# Tnh tui t nm sinh
df['Age'] = 2025 - df['Year_Birth']

# ---- 3. To th mc lu file ----
save_plot_dir = "plots_bokeh"
os.makedirs(save_plot_dir, exist_ok=True)

# ---- 4. Phn tch d liu c bn (verbose=2) ----
print("========== PHN TCH D LIU ==========")
print(df.describe(include='all'))
print("========================================\n")

# ---- 5. To biu  cho tng gi tr ca bin mc tiu ----
target_col = "Response"
if target_col in df.columns:
    unique_targets = df[target_col].unique()
else:
    unique_targets = ["All"]
    df[target_col] = "All"

for target_value in unique_targets:
    subset = df[df[target_col] == target_value]
    print(f" ang to biu  cho nhm: {target_value} (s mu: {len(subset)})")

    # To biu 
    p = figure(
        title=f"Salary vs Age - Nhm: {target_value}",
        x_axis_label="Age",
        y_axis_label="Income",
        tools="pan,wheel_zoom,box_zoom,reset,hover,save"
    )

    # HoverTool hin th thng tin
    hover = p.select(dict(type=HoverTool))
    hover.tooltips = [("Age", "@x"), ("Income", "@y"), ("Target", target_col)]

    # V scatter
    p.circle(subset['Age'], subset['Income'], size=8, color="navy", alpha=0.6)

    # ---- 6. Lu biu  ----
    output_path = os.path.join(save_plot_dir, f"bokeh_plot_{target_value}.html")
    output_file(output_path)
    save(p)

    print(f" Biu  '{target_value}'  c lu ti: {output_path}\n")

print(" Hon tt to biu  Bokeh cho tt c cc nhm mc tiu.")

SWEETVIZ
M t: SweetViz l th vin Python m ngun m chuyn to bo co EDA chi tit v p mt di dng file HTML tng tc. N ch cn 2 dng code  phn tch ton b dataset, bao gm thng k m t, phn phi d liu, mi tng quan (correlation), v so snh gia cc tp d liu (v d: train vs test).


u im:
    

  • Bo co trc quan, d c, vi h tr correlation cho c d liu s (Pearson), phn loi (uncertainty coefficient), v hn hp.
    • 

  • Xut file HTML t cha, c th m trn trnh duyt  tng tc (zoom, filter).
    • 

  • Ph hp cho phn tch su hn so vi AutoViz.
    • 























Chc nng chnh
    

  • Bo co EDA chi tit: To bo co HTML tng tc vi thng k m t (mean, median, min, max, v.v.) v phn phi cho tng ct.
    • 

  • Tng quan nng cao: Phn tch tng quan cho d liu s, phn loi, v hn hp (Pearson, uncertainty coefficient, correlation ratio).
    • 

  • So snh dataset: So snh hai dataset (v d: train vs test)  pht hin s khc bit.
    • 

  • X l gi tr thiu: Hin th t l v phn phi gi tr thiu.
    • 

  • Giao din tng tc: Bo co HTML cho php zoom, lc d liu, d chia s.
    •

# Import cc th vin cn thit
import sweetviz as sv
import pandas as pd

# Hm kim tra v lc cc ct tn ti trong DataFrame
def validate_columns(df, columns_to_check):
    # Chun ha tn ct: b khong trng tha v chuyn v ch thng
    existing_cols = df.columns.str.strip().str.lower()
    
    # Lc danh sch ct cn kim tra theo cc ct thc t c trong DataFrame
    return [col for col in columns_to_check 
            if col.strip().lower() in existing_cols]

# To cu hnh features ng theo cc ct thc t
skip_columns = validate_columns(df, ['Z_Revenue', 'Z_CostContact'])  # Cc ct cn b qua
force_text_cols = validate_columns(df, ['ID'])  # Ct cn p kiu vn bn

# Khi to cu hnh phn tch
feature_config = sv.FeatureConfig(
    skip=skip_columns,      # B qua cc ct khng tn ti
    force_text=force_text_cols  # p kiu cc ct ch nh
)

try:
    # To bo co phn tch d liu
    report = sv.analyze(
        source=df,                   # DataFrame u vo
        target_feat='Response',      # Ct mc tiu
        feat_cfg=feature_config,     # Cu hnh features
        pairwise_analysis='on'       # Bt phn tch cp
    )
    
    # Xut bo co HTML
    report.show_html(
        filepath='sweetviz_feature_config_report.html',  # ng dn lu file
        open_browser=True,    # M trnh duyt t ng
        layout='widescreen',  # Giao din rng
        scale=1.0             # T l hin th
    )
    
except ValueError as e:
    # X l li cu hnh
    print(f"Li cu hnh: {str(e)}")
    print("Danh sch ct kh dng:", df.columns.tolist())  # Hin th cc ct thc t
